    "Tables (Responsive, sortable data tables)",
    "Avatars (User profile system with badges)",
    "Loaders (Animated loading indicators)",
    "Skeletons (Loading placeholders)",
    "Carousels (Swipeable content sliders)",
    "Accordions (Collapsible content)",
    "Paginations (Numeric, progress bar)",
